7月22日，一股[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]在墨西哥近海发展成热带低气压。系统起初向西移动，于当天强化成热带风暴。<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />7月24日，受上层气旋影响，尤金转向北上，并升级成本季首场飓风<ref name="HPC">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140721041721/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/eugene1987.html | archivedate = 2014-07-21 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/eugene1987.html | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | title = Hurricane Eugene – July 22–27, 1987 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 }}</ref>。7月25日，风暴达到二级飓风强度下限<ref name="best track">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/tracks1949to2007_epa.txt | date = 2008-03-21 | title = Eastern North Pacific Tracks File 1949–2007 | accessdate = 2009-01-15 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090115064810/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/tracks1949to2007_epa.txt | archivedate = 2009-01-15 | deadurl = yes | format = TXT }}</ref>，但又因受陆地影响而减弱，以一级飓风强度从[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]以南[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。粗糙的地形令飓风减弱，气旋进入[[加利福尼亚湾|加利福尼亚湾]]时已降级成热带低气压，最终于7月26日消散。<ref name="HPC"/>

7月24日，尤金首度对墨西哥构成威胁，[[锡瓦塔内霍|锡瓦塔内霍]]港停止向小型船只开放，阿卡普尔科港暂停运作，曼萨尼约港则正式关闭。墨西哥海军下令总计1520公里地域进入警戒状态。气象机构向沿海3个州发布航海警告，政府还敦促海上船只随时保持联络。<ref name="VA">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Strikes Mexican coast | date = 1987-07-28 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MOBHAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LYAMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1295,1230588&dq=hurricane+eugene&hl=en | newspaper = Victoria Advocate | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | archive-date = 2021-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121104113/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MOBHAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LYAMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1295%2C1230588&dq=hurricane+eugene&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>飓风尤金在墨西哥沿海部分地区引发瓢泼大雨，其中以[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]的阿奎拉（{{lang|en|Aquila}}）降雨量最高，达525毫米<ref name="HPC" />。气旋在该国5个州的降雨量刷新此前热带气旋的纪录<ref name="Roth">{{cite web | author = David Roth | title = Tropical Cyclone Maxima Per Mexican State | work = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | format = GIF | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmexicostatemaxima.gif | archivedate = 2013-05-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530225227/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmexicostatemaxima.gif | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-09-02 }}</ref>。整个墨西哥有超过5000人流离失所<ref name="EB">{{cite news | title = Hurricane hits Mexican coast | newspaper = Ellensburg Daily Record | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=T_NYAAAAIBAJ&sjid=H48DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6687,2842734&dq=hurricane+eugene&hl=en | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | date = 1987-07-28 | archive-date = 2016-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160527223120/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=T_NYAAAAIBAJ&sjid=H48DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6687,2842734&dq=hurricane+eugene&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。单曼萨尼约就有60余人无家可归<ref name="UPI">{{cite news | date = 1987-07-26 | publisher = Logansport Pharos-Tribune | title = Hurricane Hits Mexico's Pacific Coast}}</ref>。风暴造成的破坏主要是四处散落的瓦砾和泥浆，全国有6人受伤，3人遇难<ref name="EB" />，其中1名男子被狂风刮倒的棕榈树砸死<ref name="Del Rio News Herald">{{cite news | newspaper = Del Rio News-Herald | date = 1987-07-28 | title = Death attributed to Hurricane Eugene}}</ref>。飓风还摧毁了墨西哥约39平方公里水果作物，损失数额超过260万美元（1987年[[美元|美元]]）<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = United Press International | title = Fruit crop suffers $2.6 million in damages}}</ref>。此外，还有8套海滨房屋受到价值12万美元的破坏<ref name="UPIIII">{{cite news | title = BC cycle | date = 2013-07-26 | agency = United Press International}}</ref>。整场风暴造成的损失总额达1亿4200万美元<ref name="Book" />。气旋过去后，墨西哥海军、陆军和地方政府制订清理计划，迅速恢复供水和供电，大部分受影响地区的水、电都在数天内恢复<ref name="EB" />。
