{{main|飓风拉蒙}}
10月3至4日，一片扰动天气区进入墨西哥中部上空高气压以南的太平洋，其组织结构在超过29°C的水温上空逐渐改善<ref name="mwr" />，到10月5日时，曼萨尼约西南方向约790公里海域已经发展出热带风暴<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />。拉蒙总体保持向西北偏西方向移动<ref name="mwr" />，于10月7日成为飓风，次日达到大型飓风标准。10月9至10日，拉蒙达到风力时速220公里的最高强度<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />。接下来，风暴因受亚热带急速气流的影响转向西北，并因水温降低而迅速弱化<ref name="mwr" />，于10月11日减弱成热带风暴，12日又降级成热带低气压，之后不久就完全消散<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />。

南加利福尼亚州暴雨成灾<ref name="news3">{{cite news | title = Snow, Record Cold Hit U.S. | page = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DT9WAAAAIBAJ&sjid=CuoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3562,3437942&dq=hurricane+california&hl=en | newspaper = The Gainesville Sun | date = 1987-10-13 | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | archive-date = 2021-01-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210103185602/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DT9WAAAAIBAJ&sjid=CuoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3562%2C3437942&dq=hurricane+california&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，引发街道洪灾<ref name="5deaths">{{cite news | title = 5 dead in S. California is Storm's last Punch | newspaper = San Jose Mercury News | date = 1987-10-13}}</ref>。有两人因交通事故丧生<ref>{{cite news | title = Dying Hurricane Sprinkles Rains to Southland | newspaper = Daily News of Los Angeles | date = 1987-10-13}}</ref>。[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]另有3人因交通事故遇难<ref name="news4">{{cite news | title = Storm Brings Record Rain | page = 5 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XyFZAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zUYNAAAAIBAJ&pg=4856,1678895&dq=hurricane+california&hl=en | newspaper = The Union Democrat | date = 1987-10-13 | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | archive-date = 2021-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121104156/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XyFZAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zUYNAAAAIBAJ&pg=4856%2C1678895&dq=hurricane+california&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[河滨县|河滨县]]的[[赫米特_(加利福尼亚州)|赫米特]]也出现暴雨<ref name="news4" />，有3人因车祸受伤<ref name="LN">{{cite news | title = Cold on the Plains, Snow on Vermont | date = 1987-10-13 | agency = United Press International}}</ref>。降水有助于消除[[帕洛马山|帕洛马山]]持续一周，影响面积达6500万平方米的森林大火<ref name="news4" />。春溪河溢出堤防<ref>{{cite news | title = San Jose Mercury News (CA) – October 13, 1987 – 8B California News  Record San Diego Area Rains Help Control Big Brush Fire | date = 1987-10-13 | newspaper = San Jose Mercury news}}</ref>。拉蒙的热带水分还有助于结束[[盐湖城|盐湖城]]持续37天的旱情，这也是该市1964年来持续最久的旱情。全美共有5人因这场风暴遇害，均为道路相关事故引发。<ref name="LN2">{{cite news | title = Domestic News | date = 1987-10-13 | agency = Associated Press}}</ref>
